dise-jannah","tag-remembrance-al-dhikr","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9HE","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/01\/dua-loudly-allah-sami\/","url_meta":{"origin":37302,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Do not supplicate so loudly, Allah is Hearing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: We were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on a journey when the people began to exalt Allah loudly. The Prophet said, \u201cO people, be gentle with yourselves! You are not calling upon one who is deaf or absent, rather you are calling upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34821,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/adhan-sunan-responding\/","url_meta":{"origin":37302,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Sunan of responding to the call to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the caller to prayer says, \u2018Allah is the greatest, Allah is the greatest,\u2019 then let one of you say, \u2018Allah is the greatest, Allah is the greatest.\u2019 Then he says, \u2018I testify there is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/11\/99-names-allah-asma-al-husna\/","url_meta":{"origin":37302,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on 99 Names: Whoever acts upon them enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has ninety-nine names. Whoever preserves\u00a0them will enter Paradise.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7392, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2677 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":268,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/14\/faith-truly-knows-allah-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":37302,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Whoever truly knows Allah enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever died truly knowing that there is no God but Allah will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 26 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645\u200f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22127,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/03\/02\/ilm-path-knowledge-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37302,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Path in search of knowledge leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever travels a path in search of knowledge, Allah will make easy for him a path to Paradise.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2699 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \